targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  g1.timestamp,
  (
    FLOOR(substring(g1.value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric / 100) + 
    ((substring(g1.value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric - (FLOOR(substring(g1.value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric / 100) * 100)) / 60)
  ) * -1 AS latitude, 

  (
    FLOOR(substring(g2.value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric / 100) + 
    ((substring(g2.value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric - (FLOOR(substring(g2.value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric / 100) * 100)) / 60)
  ) AS longitude
FROM gnss g1
JOIN gnss g2 
  ON g1.timestamp = g2.timestamp 
  AND g1.gnss_id = g2.gnss_id
WHERE g1.sensor_id LIKE 'LAT%'  
  AND g2.sensor_id LIKE 'LON%' 
  AND g1.value ~ '[0-9]+\.[0-9]+'
  AND g2.value ~ '[0-9]+\.[0-9]+'
  AND g1.gnss_id = '$gnss_id'  
  AND g1.value IS NOT NULL
  AND g1.value <> ''
  AND g2.value IS NOT NULL
  AND g2.value <> ''
  AND $__timeFilter(g1.timestamp)
  ORDER BY g1.timestamp DESC
LIMIT 1000;

SELECT (
    FLOOR(substring(value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric / 100) + 
    ((substring(value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric - (FLOOR(substring(value from '([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)')::numeric / 100) * 100)) / 60)
  ) as longitude,
  gnss_id, 
  sensor_id, 
  timestamp
FROM gnss
WHERE gnss_id = '$gnss_id'
  AND sensor_id LIKE 'LON%'
  AND value ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$'  
   AND value IS NOT NULL
  AND value <> ''
  AND $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  ORDER BY timestamp DESC
LIMIT 5;

SELECT gnss_id, timestamp, CAST(value AS DOUBLE PRECISION) as "value", sensor_id
FROM gnss
WHERE gnss_id = '$gnss_id'
  AND value ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$'    
  AND $__timeFilter(timestamp)
ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 1000
